data.name: Potion
rules: You may play any number of Item cards during your turn.
Heal 30 damage from 1 of your Pokémon.

data.name: PlusPower
rules: You may play as many Item cards as you like during your turn (before your attack).
"During this turn, your Pokémons attacks do 10 more damage to the Active Pokémon (before applying Weakness and Resistance)."

data.name: Switch
rules: You may play any number of Item cards during your turn.
Switch your Active Pokémon with 1 of your Benched Pokémon.

data.name: Pokémon Catcher
rules: You may play any number of Item cards during your turn.
"Flip a coin. If heads, switch 1 of your opponents Benched Pokémon with their Active Pokémon."

data.name: Poké Ball
rules: You may play any number of Item cards during your turn.
Flip a coin. If heads, search your deck for a Pokémon, reveal it, and put it into your hand. Then, shuffle your deck.

data.name: Professor Oak's Meeting
rules: You may play only 1 Supporter card during your turn (before your attack).
